testcase.name: User creates an Amplitude X source
testcase.system-out: ✅ Given I open the site "/login"✅ And I log in with "enterprise" account✅ And I visit the url "/directory"✅ When I add a source of type "Amplitude" with name "Src_Amp" with details✅ Then I expect to be in the "Src_Amp" page

testcase.name: User creates a Snowflake warehouse destination
testcase.system-out: ✅ And I visit the url "/directory"✅ When I add a destination of type "Snowflake" with name "Dst_SNFLK" with details✅ Then I expect to be in the "Dst_SNFLK" page

testcase.name: User removes connection deletes warehouse destination
testcase.system-out: ✅ Given I navigate to destination "Dst_SNFLK"✅ When I disconnect source "Src_Amp" from destination✅ And I delete the current destination✅ Then I expect to be in the "Destinations" page

testcase.name: User deletes X source
testcase.system-out: ✅ Given I navigate to source "Src_Amp"✅ When I delete the current source✅ Then I expect to be in the "Sources" page
